<script type="text/javascript">
        var hasMMY = false;
        var hasTE = false;
        var year = 0;
        var make = '';
        var model = '';
        var mmyID = 0;
        var trim = '';
        var engine = '';
                
        var onCompleteCallBack;
        var service = new MMYService();
        if (service)
        {
            if (!hasMMY)
            {
                onCompleteCallBack = Function.createDelegate(this, recieveYears);
                service.getYears(onCompleteCallBack);
            }
            else
            {
                
                if (hasMMY && !hasTE && showte)
                {
                    onCompleteCallBack = Function.createDelegate(this, recieveTrims);
                    //service.getTrims(year, make, model, onCompleteCallBack);
                    service.getTrims(mmyID, onCompleteCallBack);
                }
                else
                {
                    
                }
            }
        }

        function recieveYears (values)
        {
            generateoptions('ddlYear', 'Year', values);
            emptyoptions('ddlMake', 'Make');
            emptyoptions('ddlModel', 'Model');            
            emptyoptions('ddlTrim', 'Trim');
            emptyoptions('ddlEngine', 'Engine');
            spinner(false);
        }
        function recieveMakes (values)
        {
            generateoptions('ddlMake', 'Make', values);
            spinner(false);
        }
        function recieveModels (values)
        {
            generateoptions('ddlModel', 'Model', values);
            spinner(false);
        }
        function recieveTrims(values)
        {
            generateoptions('ddlTrim', 'Trim', values);
            emptyoptions('ddlEngine', 'Engine');
            spinner(false);
        }
        function recieveEngines(values)
        {
            generateoptions('ddlEngine', 'Engine', values);
            spinner(false);
        }


        function mmySaved ()
        {
            window.location.href = 'e-mmyproducts.aspx';
        }

        function generateoptions (name, type, values)
        {
            var options = "<option value='0'>Select " + type + " ...</option>";
            for (var i = 0; i < values.length; i++)
            {
                options += "<option value='" + values[i] + "'>" + values[i] + "</option>";
            }
            $('#' + name).html("");
            $('#' + name).append(options);
        }

        function emptyoptions (name, type)
        {
            var options = "<option value='0'>Choose " + type + " ...</option>";
            $('#' + name).html(options);
        }


        function YearSelector_onChange(select)
        {
            emptyoptions('ddlMake', 'Make');
            emptyoptions('ddlModel', 'Model');            
            emptyoptions('ddlTrim', 'Trim');
            emptyoptions('ddlEngine', 'Engine');
            if (select.value != '0')
            {
                if (service)
                {
                    spinner(true);
                    year = select.value;
                    onCompleteCallBack = Function.createDelegate(this, recieveMakes);
                    service.getMakes(year, onCompleteCallBack);
                }
            }
        }

        function MakeSelector_onChange(select)
        {
            emptyoptions('ddlModel', 'Model');
            emptyoptions('ddlTrim', 'Trim');
            emptyoptions('ddlEngine', 'Engine');
            if (select.value != '0')
            {
                if (service)
                {
                    spinner(true);
                    make = select.value;
                    onCompleteCallBack = Function.createDelegate(this, recieveModels);
                    service.getModels(year, make, onCompleteCallBack);
                }
            }
        }

        function ModelSelector_onChange(select)
        {
            emptyoptions('ddlTrim', 'Trim');
            emptyoptions('ddlEngine', 'Engine');
            if (select.value != '0')
            {
                if (service)
                {
                    spinner(true);
                    model = select.value;
                    onCompleteCallBack = Function.createDelegate(this, mmySaved);
                    service.saveMMY(year, make, model, onCompleteCallBack);
                }
            }
        }

        function TrimSelector_onChange(select)
        {
            emptyoptions('ddlEngine', 'Engine');
            if (select.value != '0')
            {
                if (service)
                {
                    spinner(true);
                    trim = select.value;
                    onCompleteCallBack = Function.createDelegate(this, recieveEngines);
                    service.getEngines(mmyID, trim, onCompleteCallBack);
                }
            }
        }

        function EngineSelector_onChange(select)
        {
            if (select.value != '0')
            {
                if (service)
                {
                    spinner(true);
                    engine = select.value;
                    onCompleteCallBack = Function.createDelegate(this, mmySaved);
                    service.saveMMYTE(year, make, model, trim, engine, onCompleteCallBack);
                }
            }
        }

        function spinner(show)
        {
            if (show)
                $("#MMYspinnner").show();
            else
                $("#MMYspinnner").hide();
        }
    </script>

<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: center;"><strong id="jumptobottom">Car Light</strong></p>
<br/>
All the lighting and reflectivity components of an automobile are meant to provide illumination so you can operate your vehicle safely. This means allowing you to see in the dark, increasing your vehicles perceptibility, and allowing other drivers to accurately detect your presence including speed, position, size, and direction of travel. Many avoidable accidents take place because light malfunctions or breakdowns, so it pays to take proper care of your car lighting system and components.
<div><br/>
</div>
<div><strong>Are you in need of new car light parts and components?</strong> ALL of our car lights are direct fit and designed for vehicle specific application on all makes and models. To ensure absolute safety while you are operating your vehicle, all of your car&rsquo;s lighting components have to be functioning properly all of the time. Prime Choice Auto Parts offers a variety of car lights parts at discount prices. For any questions call 1 866 990 3871 to speak with one of our friendly customer service specialists.
</div></div>
